videos.description: Xavier Sneed intercepts a pass in the back-court, and takes it all the way for a big two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Sneed steals and slams

videos.description: Barry Brown Jr. anticipates the pass and picks it off, taking it the length of the floor for an electrifying finish.
videos.headline: Brown turns defense into offense

videos.description: Kamau Stokes steals a pass and whips an outlet pass to Barry Brown Jr., who saves it from going out of bounds before finishing an and-1.
videos.headline: Brown saves ball to score in transition
